"(:guilabel:`navpične tri pike`), nato :icon:`fa-tag` :guilabel:`Popust`. "
"Nastavite odstotek popusta in kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:31
msgid "Line discounts"
msgstr "Vrstični popusti"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:33
msgid ""
"To set a discount on a specific product, select the product from the cart, "
"click the :guilabel:`%` cart modifier from the pad, then use the numpad to "
"set the discount."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti popust na določen izdelek, izberite izdelek iz košarice, "
"kliknite modifikator košarice :guilabel:`%` na tipkovnici, nato uporabite "
"številčnico za nastavitev popusta."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:37
