#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:45
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:3
msgid "Discount and loyalty programs"
msgstr "Programi popustov in zvestobe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:47
msgid ""
"Discount and loyalty programs provide flexible, customer-facing pricing "
"strategies. Unlike :doc:`pricelists <../../sales/products_prices/prices/"
"pricing>`, which define structured pricing rules, discount and loyalty "
"programs are designed for promotional, time-sensitive, and public offers, "
"such as seasonal sales, limited-time deals, or customer rewards."
msgstr ""
"Programi popustov in zvestobe zagotavljają prilagodljive, na stranke "
"usmerjene strategije oblikovanja cen. Za razliko od :doc:`cenikov <../../"
"sales/products_prices/prices/pricing>`, ki določajo strukturirana pravila za "
"oblikovanje cen, so programi popustov in zvestobe namenjeni promocijskim, "
"časovno omejenim in javnim ponudbam, kot so sezonske razprodaje, časovno "
"omejene ponudbe ali nagrade za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:52
msgid ""
"To activate discount and loyalty programs in Point of Sale, navigate to "
"the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Pricing` section, and enable :guilabel:`Promotions, Coupons, "
"Gift Card & Loyalty Program`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati programe popustov in zvestobe v Prodajni točki, pojdite "
"v :ref:`nastavitve POS <pos/use/settings>`, pomaknite se navzdol do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Oblikovanje cen` in omogočite :guilabel:`Promocije, kuponi, "
"darilne kartice in program zvestobe`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:56
msgid ""
"Once the feature has been activated, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Products --> Discount & Loyalty` and :ref:`configure the desired discount "
"and loyalty programs <sales/products/loyalty-programs>`. These programs are "
"triggered when an order meets the defined requirements. Depending on "
"the :ref:`program type <sales/pricing_management/program-types>`, rewards "
"are either applied automatically or manually by the cashier."
msgstr ""
"Ko je funkcija aktivirana, pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> "
"Izdelki --> Popusti in zvestoba` ter :ref:`konfigurirajte želene programe "
"popustov in zvestobe <sales/products/loyalty-programs>`. Ti programi se "
"sprožijo, ko naročilo izpolni določene zahteve. Glede na :ref:`vrsto "
"programa <sales/pricing_management/program-types>` se nagrade uporabijo "
"samodejno ali ročno s strani blagajnika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:63
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:68
msgid "Codes"
msgstr "Kode"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:70
msgid ""
"To apply a gift card, discount code, or coupon, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, select :icon:`fa-"
"barcode` :guilabel:`Enter Code`, enter or scan the code, and "
"click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti darilno kartico, kodo za popust ali kupon, kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`navpična tripičje`), izberite "
":icon:`fa-barcode` :guilabel:`Vnesi kodo`, vnesite ali skenirajte kodo in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:75
msgid ""
"Coupon and next-order coupon codes are printed directly on customer receipts."
msgstr ""
"Kode kuponov in kuponov za naslednje naročilo so natisnjene neposredno na "
"potrdilih strank."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:78
msgid "Promotions"
msgstr "Promocije"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:80
msgid ""
"Promotions are fully automated. They are applied to the order as soon as all "
"program conditions (such as minimum spent or specific products) are met."
msgstr ""
"Promocije so popolnoma avtomatizirane. Uporabijo se za naročilo takoj, ko so "
"izpolnjeni vsi pogoji programa (npr. minimalna poraba ali določeni izdelki)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:84
msgid "Buy X get Y"
msgstr "Kupi X dobi Y"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:86
msgid ""
"When the order qualifies for a **Buy X get Y** deal, the reward must be "
"added manually. Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical "
"ellipsis`) icon, select :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`Reward`, and choose the "
"desired item from the list."
msgstr ""
"Ko je naročilo upravičeno do ponudbe **Kupi X dobi Y**, je treba nagrado "
"dodati ročno. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`navpična "
"tripičje`), izberite :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`Nagrada` in s seznama "
"izberite želeni artikel."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:91
msgid "Loyalty cards"
msgstr "Kartice zvestobe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:93
msgid ""
"To track or spend loyalty points, you must first :ref:`select a customer "
"<pos/use/customers>` in the POS register. Once selected, "
"their :guilabel:`Loyalty point(s)` are displayed at the bottom of the cart "
"and updated in real-time."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremljati ali porabiti točke zvestobe, morate najprej "
":ref:`izbrati stranko <pos/use/customers>` v blagajni POS. Ko je izbrana, so "
"njene :guilabel:`Točke zvestobe` prikazane na dnu košarice in posodobljene v "
"realnem času."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:97
msgid ""
"To redeem points for a reward, click the :icon:`oi-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, select :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`Reward`, and choose the desired item from the list."
msgstr ""
"Če želite unovčiti točke za nagrado, kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`navpična tripičje`), izberite :icon:`fa-star` "
":guilabel:`Nagrada` in s seznama izberite želeni artikel."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:103
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:3
msgid "Pricelists"
msgstr "Ceniki"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:105
msgid ""
"Pricelists allow you to automate price adjustments based on specific "
"criteria. They can be used to set POS-specific prices, create temporary "
"discount periods, reward loyal customers, or offer bulk-buy discounts."
msgstr ""
"Ceniki omogočajo avtomatizacijo prilagoditev cen na podlagi določenih meril. "
"Lahko se uporabljajo za nastavitev cen, specifičnih za POS, ustvarjanje "
"začasnih obdobij popustov, nagrajevanje zvestih strank ali ponujanje "
"popustov za množični nakup."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:112
msgid "To enable pricelists in the Point of Sale app:"
msgstr "Če želite omogočiti cenike v aplikaciji Prodajna točka:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:114
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:115
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Pricing` section, activate the :guilabel:`Flexible "
"Pricelists` feature and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Oblikovanje cen` aktivirajte funkcijo "
":guilabel:`Prilagodljivi ceniki` in :guilabel:`Shranite`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:117
msgid ""
"Once the page reloads, click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Pricelists` "
"to :ref:`configure the pricelists <sales/products/pricelist-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko se stran ponovno naloži, kliknite :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Ceniki`, da :ref:`konfigurirate cenike <sales/products/pricelist-"
"configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:119
msgid ""
"When configured, return to the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>` to add "
"all relevant pricelists to the :guilabel:`Available` field, and select the "
"one to be used as the :guilabel:`Default`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so konfigurirani, se vrnite v :ref:`nastavitve POS <pos/use/settings>`, "
"da dodate vse ustrezne cenike v polje :guilabel:`Na voljo` in izberite "
"tistega, ki naj se uporabi kot :guilabel:`Privzeti`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:124
msgid "Assign pricelists"
msgstr "Dodelite cenike"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:126
msgid ""
"To manually assign a pricelist to an order from the :ref:`POS register <pos/"
"use/open-register>`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical "
"ellipsis`) icon and the :icon:`fa-th-list` icon, followed by the currently "
"selected pricelist's name. Then, click the new pricelist to apply."
msgstr ""
"Če želite cenika ročno dodeliti naročilu iz :ref:`POS registra <pos/use/open-"
"register>`, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`navpična tri "
"pika`) in ikono :icon:`fa-th-list`, nato pa ime trenutno izbranega cenika. "
"Nato kliknite novi cenik, ki ga želite uporabiti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:131
msgid ""
"You can also set a pricelist to be selected automatically for a "
"specific :ref:`customer <pos/use/customers>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Customers`, select the "
"relevant customer, and assign a pricelist in the :guilabel:`Pricelist` field "
"of the :guilabel:`Sales` section in the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab."
msgstr ""
"Cenika lahko nastavite tudi tako, da se samodejno izbere za določenega "
":ref:`stranko <pos/use/customers>`. Če želite to narediti, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Naročila --> Stranke`, izberite ustrezno "
"stranko in dodelite cenik v polju :guilabel:`Cenik` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Prodaja` na zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:137
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:138
msgid ":ref:`Pricelists in eCommerce <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Ceniki v e-trgovini <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:143
msgid "Cash rounding"
msgstr "Gotovinsko zaokroževanje"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:145
msgid ""
"Cash rounding is used when the smallest physical currency denomination (the "
"smallest coin) is higher than the minimum unit of account."
msgstr ""
"Zaokroževanje gotovine se uporablja, kadar je najmanjša fizična denarna "
"enota (najmanjši kovanec) večja od najmanjše obračunske enote."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:148
msgid ""
"For example, in countries that have phased out one-cent and two-cent coins, "
"businesses must round the total amount of a cash transaction to the nearest "
"five cents. In Odoo, each point of sale can be individually configured to "
"apply these rounding rules to bills and receipts."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, v državah, ki so opustile kovance za en cent in dva centa, morajo "
"podjetja zaokrožiti skupni znesek gotovinske transakcije na najbližjih pet "
"centov. V Odoo lahko vsako prodajno točko posamezno konfigurirate, da na "
"račune in potrdila uporablja ta pravila zaokroževanja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:155
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/receipt_printers.rst:38
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:144
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:156
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Payment` section, enable :guilabel:`Cash Rounding`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Plačilo` omogočite :guilabel:`Zaokroževanje gotovine`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:157
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Apply only on cash methods` to deactivate rounding "
"for :doc:`card payments <../payment_methods>`."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite :guilabel:`Uporabi samo za gotovinske metode`, če želite "
"onemogočiti zaokroževanje za :doc:`plačila s kartico <../payment_methods>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:159
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Rounding Method` field, select an existing method or "
"click :guilabel:`Create` to define a new one."
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Metoda zaokroževanja` izberite obstoječo metodo ali "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`, da določite novo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:162
msgid "When creating a new rounding method, define the following:"
msgstr "Pri ustvarjanju nove metode zaokroževanja določite naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:164
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rounding Precision`: The value of the smallest coinage available "
"(e.g., 0.05)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Natančnost zaokroževanja`: Vrednost najmanjšega razpoložljivega "
"kovanca (npr. 0,05)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:165
msgid ":guilabel:`Rounding Strategy`: Choose how the adjustment is recorded:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Strategija zaokroževanja`: Izberite, kako se zabeleži "
"prilagoditev:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Modify tax amount`: The rounding difference is applied in the "
"taxes section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spremeni znesek davka`: Razlika pri zaokroževanju se uporabi v "
"razdelku davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:168
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a rounding line`: The rounding difference is added as a "
"separate line on the receipt and the invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico zaokroževanja`: Razlika pri zaokroževanju se doda "
"kot ločena vrstica na potrdilu in računu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Profit Account` and :guilabel:`Loss Account`: The accounts used "
"to record the rounding discrepancies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Konto dobička` in :guilabel:`Konto izgube`: Konti, uporabljeni za "
"beleženje razlik pri zaokroževanju."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:172
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rounding Method`: The tie-breaking rule used to determine the "
"direction of the rounding (:guilabel:`Up`, :guilabel:`Down`, "
"or :guilabel:`Nearest`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Metoda zaokroževanja`: Pravilo za odločanje o smeri zaokroževanja "
"(:guilabel:`Navzgor`, :guilabel:`Navzdol` ali :guilabel:`Najbližje`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:176
msgid ""
"Odoo Point of Sale only supports the :guilabel:`Add a rounding line` "
"rounding strategy."
msgstr ""
"Prodajna točka Odoo podpira samo strategijo zaokroževanja :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"vrstico za zaokroževanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:180
msgid "Example: Rounding a $19.92 total with a **rounding precision** of 0.05."
msgstr ""
"Primer: Zaokroževanje skupnega zneska 19,92 USD z **natančnostjo "
"zaokroževanja** 0,05."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:182
msgid ""
"The final total changes depending on the **rounding method** selected in the "
"configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Končni skupni znesek se spremeni glede na **metodo zaokroževanja**, izbrano "
"v konfiguraciji:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:190
msgid "Rounding method"
msgstr "Metoda zaokroževanja"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:191
msgid "Resulting total"
msgstr "Končni skupni znesek"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:192
msgid "Logic"
msgstr "Logika"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:193
msgid ":guilabel:`Up`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Navzgor`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:194
msgid "$19.95"
msgstr "$19.95"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:195
msgid "Always rounds toward the higher value."
msgstr "Vedno zaokroži navzgor."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:196
msgid ":guilabel:`Down`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Navzdol`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:197
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:200
msgid "$19.90"
msgstr "$19.90"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:198
msgid "Always rounds toward the lower value."
msgstr "Vedno zaokroži navzdol."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:199
msgid ":guilabel:`Nearest`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Najbližje`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:201
msgid "Rounds to the nearest 0.05."
msgstr "Zaokroži na najbližjih 0,05."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:204
msgid ""
"Rounding only applies to the **Total** of the receipt, not to individual "
"product prices."
msgstr ""
"Zaokroževanje velja le za **skupni znesek** računa, ne za posamezne cene "
"izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:209
msgid "Flexible taxes (fiscal positions)"
msgstr "Prilagodljivi davki (davčni položaji)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:211
msgid ""
"When running a business, you may need to apply different taxes and record "
"transactions on various accounts based on the location and type of business "
"of your customers and providers."
msgstr ""
"Pri vodenju podjetja boste morda morali uporabiti različne davke in beležiti "
"transakcije na različne račune glede na lokacijo in vrsto poslovanja vaših "
"strank in dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:214
msgid ""
"Fiscal positions allow you to define rules that automatically select the "
"appropriate taxes and accounts used for each transaction."
msgstr ""
"Davčni položaji vam omogočajo določitev pravil, ki samodejno izberejo "
"ustrezne davke in račune za vsako transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:218
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:219
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/taxes`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/taxes`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:224
msgid ""
"To use fiscal positions, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Accounting` "
"section, and enable :guilabel:`Flexible Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti davčne položaje, pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna "
"točka --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite navzdol do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Računovodstvo` in omogočite :guilabel:`Prilagodljivi davki`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:227
msgid "Then, configure the fiscal position for your POS:"
msgstr "Nato konfigurirajte davčni položaj za vašo prodajno točko:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:229
msgid ""
"Set the default fiscal position to be automatically applied to all sales in "
"the selected POS using the :guilabel:`Default` field."
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Privzeto` nastavite privzeti davčni položaj, ki bo "
"samodejno uporabljen za vse prodaje v izbrani prodajni točki."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:231
msgid ""
"Select additional fiscal positions in the :guilabel:`Allowed` field to make "
"them selectable during sales."
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Dovoljeno` izberite dodatne davčne položaje, da bodo na "
"voljo med prodajo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:234
msgid ""
"Depending on the installed :doc:`fiscal localization package </applications/"
"finance/fiscal_localizations>`, several fiscal positions are already "
"preconfigured and ready to use in the POS. You can also :ref:`create new "
"ones <fiscal_positions/configuration>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od nameščenega :doc:`paketa za davčno lokalizacijo </applications/"
"finance/fiscal_localizations>`, je več davčnih položajev že vnaprej "
"konfiguriranih in pripravljenih za uporabo v prodajni točki. Po potrebi "
"lahko :ref:`ustvarite nove <fiscal_positions/configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:240
msgid ""
":ref:`A default fiscal position can also be assigned to a customer "
"<accounting/fiscal_positions/partner>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Privzeti davčni položaj lahko dodelite tudi stranki <accounting/"
"fiscal_positions/partner>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:242
msgid ""
"If no fiscal position is configured, the tax defined in the "
"product's :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` field is applied."
msgstr ""
"Če davčni položaj ni konfiguriran, se uporabi davek, določen v polju "
":guilabel:`Prodajni davki` izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:246
msgid "Apply fiscal positions"
msgstr "Uporaba davčnih položajev"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:248
msgid ""
"To apply a fiscal position to a POS order in the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/"
"open-register>`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical "
"ellipsis`) icon, click the :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Tax` button, and "
"choose the desired fiscal position from the list."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v :ref:`registru prodajne točke <pos/use/open-register>` uporabiti "
"davčni položaj za naročilo, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`navpična tri pika`), kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-book` "
":guilabel:`Davek` in s seznama izberite želeni davčni položaj."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:5
msgid ""
"The self-ordering feature allows customers to browse your menu or product "
"catalog, place an order, and complete payment using their mobile device or a "
"self-ordering kiosk."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija samopolstrežnega naročanja strankam omogoča brskanje po vašem "
"meniju ali katalogu izdelkov, oddajo naročila in dokončanje plačila z "
"uporabo svoje mobilne naprave ali samopolstrežnega kioska."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:12
msgid "Feature activation"
msgstr "Aktivacija funkcije"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:14
msgid ""
"To enable this feature and select a self-ordering type, access the :ref:`POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Mobile self-"
"order & Kiosk` section, and select a :guilabel:`Self Ordering` type under "
"the :guilabel:`QR menu & Kiosk activation` section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo in izbrati vrsto samopomožnega naročanja, "
"odprite :ref:`nastavitve prodajne točke <pos/use/settings>`, pomaknite se "
"navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`Mobilno samopomožno naročanje in kiosk` ter v "
