#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/epos_ssc.rst:59
msgid ""
"On the EPSON platform, click :guilabel:`Advanced Settings`, "
"then :guilabel:`Administrator Login` to log in to the printer's homepage."
