msgstr ""
"Z desno miškino tipko kliknite na datoteke s potrdili in izberite "
":guilabel:`Install Certificate`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:89
msgid ""
"Specify the certificate location and select the installation scope: either "
"the :guilabel:`Current User` only or all users (:guilabel:`Local Machine`). "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Določite lokacijo potrdila in izberite obseg namestitve: bodisi samo "
":guilabel:`Current User` ali vsi uporabniki (:guilabel:`Local Machine`). "
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:92
msgid ""
"On the `Certificate Store` screen, tick :guilabel:`Place all certificates in "
"the following store`, click :guilabel:`Browse...`, and "
