msgstr ""
"Na zaslonu `Certificate Store` označite :guilabel:`Place all certificates in "
"the following store`, kliknite :guilabel:`Browse...` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Trusted Root Certification Authorities`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:95
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Finish` and accept the pop-up security window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Finish` in sprejmite pojavno okno z varnostnim "
"opozorilom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:96
