"terminals <https://www.pinelabs.com/contact-sales?"
"tab=new&form=instorepayments>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Pine Labs <https://www.pinelabs.com/instore-pos-machine>`_ ponuja rešitve "
"za plačevanje v trgovini za transakcije strank prek več `fizičnih terminalov "
"<https://www.pinelabs.com/contact-sales?tab=new&form=instorepayments>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/pine_labs.rst:10
