#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:21
msgid "Create a POS"
msgstr "Ustvarite prodajno točko"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:23
msgid ""
"If no point of sale exists in the database, a set of POS cards is displayed "
"on the Point of Sale :guilabel:`Dashboard`. Each card represents a business "
"type. Click a card to create a POS with preconfigured settings tailored to "
"that type. These settings can be adjusted later as needed."
msgstr ""
"Če v bazi podatkov ni nobene prodajne točke, je na nadzorni plošči "
":guilabel:`Nadzorna plošča` prodajne točke prikazan niz kartic. Vsaka "
"kartica predstavlja vrsto poslovanja. Kliknite kartico, da ustvarite "
"prodajno točko s prednastavljenimi nastavitvami, prilagojenimi tej vrsti. Te "
"nastavitve lahko pozneje po potrebi prilagodite."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:27
msgid ""
"To create additional POS or to create one from scratch, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Point of Sales`, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and type a name. Additionally, "
"click :guilabel:`Configurations > Settings` to fully configure the point of "
"sale."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje dodatnih prodajnih točk ali za ustvarjanje ene od začetka "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Konfiguracija --> Prodajne "
"točke`, kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` in vnesite ime. Poleg tega kliknite "
":guilabel:`Konfiguracije > Nastavitve`, da v celoti konfigurirate prodajno "
"točko."

