"pojdite na :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`, se "
"pomaknite navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`Accounting` in izberite ustrezne "
"dnevnike v poljih :guilabel:`Orders` in :guilabel:`Invoices` pod "
":guilabel:`Default Journals`."

