msgstr ":doc:`service_products`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:121
msgid "`Tutorial: Configuring a rental product <configure-rental-product_>`_"
msgstr "`Vadnica: Konfiguracija najemnega izdelka <configure-rental-product_>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:124
msgid "Rental periods"
msgstr "Obdobja najema"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:126
msgid ""
"A rental period is the unit of time used to calculate the rental rate. This "
"setting is configured on the *Rental prices* tab on the product form. To "
"edit a default rental rate, navigate to :menuselection:`Rental app --> "
"Configuration --> Rental Periods`."
msgstr ""
"Obdobje najema je časovna enota, ki se uporablja za izračun stopnje najema. "
"Ta nastavitev je konfigurirana na zavihku *Cene najema* na obrazcu izdelka. "
"Za urejanje privzete stopnje najema pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Najem --> Konfiguracija --> Obdobja najema`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:130
msgid ""
"Select a rental period to open the *Period* form. With the exception of "
"the :guilabel:`Nightly` rental period, all period forms have the following "
"fields:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite obdobje najema, da odprete obrazec *Obdobje*. Z izjemo najemnega "
"obdobja :guilabel:`Nočno` imajo vsi obrazci obdobij naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:133
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: A short description or title for the period."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime`: Kratek opis ali naziv obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration`: The minimum amount of time before the rule is applied. "
"Set to `0` to represent a fixed rental price."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Trajanje`: Minimalni čas, preden se pravilo uporabi. Nastavite na "
"`0` za fiksno ceno najema."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unit`: A drop-down list of time periods the shortest being Hours "
"and the longest is Years."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Enota`: Spustni seznam časovnih obdobij, kjer je najkrajše ure, "
"najdaljše pa leta."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:139
msgid "To create a new rental period, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr "Za ustvarjanje novega obdobja najema kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:142
msgid "Nightly rental period"
msgstr "Nočno obdobje najema"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/product_type.rst:144
msgid ""
"The *Nightly* rental period form replaces the :guilabel:`Duration` field "
"with two new fields :guilabel:`Check-in` and :guilabel:`Check-out`. Both "
"fields use a 24-hour clock to set the time. This setting is recommended for "
"space or storage rentals that require specific times to begin and end the "
"rental period."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec najemnega obdobja *Nočno* nadomesti polje :guilabel:`Trajanje` z "
"dvema novima poljema :guilabel:`Prijava` in :guilabel:`Odjava`. Obe polji "
"uporabljata 24-urno uro za nastavitev časa. Ta nastavitev je priporočljiva "
"za najeme prostorov ali skladišč, ki zahtevajo določene čase za začetek in "
"konec najemnega obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:3
msgid "Physical rental products"
msgstr "Fizični najemni izdelki"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Rental** app allows users to customize scheduling, pricing, and "
"inventory for physical rental products that require stock movement, "
"otherwise known as *Goods*. Users can set up multiple pickup and drop-off "
"locations and track rental products by serial number."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo **Najem** uporabnikom omogoča prilagajanje razporeda, cen in "
"zaloge za fizične najemne izdelke, ki zahtevajo gibanje zalog, znane tudi "
"kot *Blago*. Uporabniki lahko nastavijo več lokacij za prevzem in vrnitev "
"ter sledijo najemnim izdelkom po serijski številki."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:14
msgid ""
"The **Rental** app offers many app-integration features. Depending on the "
"installed Odoo apps, specific settings are available. To learn more about "
"the default setting for rental products, refer to the :ref:`Settings <rental/"
"product_type/settings>` section of the *Rental product type* page. The "
"following configurations assume the **Rental** and **Inventory** apps are "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija **Najem** ponuja številne funkcije za integracijo z aplikacijami. "
"Odvisno od nameščenih aplikacij Odoo so na voljo določene nastavitve. Če "
"želite izvedeti več o privzeti nastavitvi za najemne izdelke, glejte "
"razdelek :ref:`Nastavitve <rental/product_type/settings>` na strani *Vrsta "
"najemnega izdelka*. Naslednje konfiguracije predpostavljajo, da sta "
"nameščeni aplikaciji **Najem** in **Zaloga**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:19
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Rental app --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"configure the :guilabel:`Default Delay Costs` in the *Rental* section for "
"late fees. Optionally, configure the :guilabel:`Default Padding Time` to "
"make rentals unavailable for booking. Refer to the :ref:`rental/products/"
"rental-transfer-feature` section to learn what it does and how to configure "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`aplikacija Najem --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`, v razdelku *Najem* konfigurirajte :guilabel:`Privzete stroške "
"zamude` za zamudnine. Po želji konfigurirajte :guilabel:`Privzeti varnostni "
"čas`, da najemov ne bo mogoče rezervirati. Glejte razdelek :ref:`rental/"
"products/rental-transfer-feature`, da izveste, kaj počne in kako ga "
"konfigurirati."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:25
msgid ""
"In the **Rental** section, under the :guilabel:`Default Delay Costs` "
"subsection, fill in the :guilabel:`Apply after` field."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku **Rental**, v podrazdelku :guilabel:`Default Delay Costs`, "
"izpolnite polje :guilabel:`Apply after`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:29
msgid ""
"For more control, configure the costs of late returns in the :guilabel:`Per "
"Hour` and :guilabel:`Per Day` fields on the product form. If the defaults "
"apply to all products, leave the :guilabel:`Product` field blank."
msgstr ""
"Za večji nadzor konfigurirajte stroške poznih vračil v poljih :guilabel:`Na "
"uro` in :guilabel:`Na dan` na obrazcu izdelka. Če se privzete vrednosti "
"uporabljajo za vse izdelke, pustite polje :guilabel:`Izdelek` prazno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:33
msgid "Click **Save** to apply the changes."
msgstr "Kliknite **Save** za uveljavitev sprememb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:None
msgid ""
"Example of configured Default Delay Cost and Padding settings in the Rental "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Primer konfiguriranih nastavitev privzetih stroškov zamude in varnostnega "
"časa v aplikaciji Najem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:41
msgid "Create a new physical product"
msgstr "Ustvarite nov fizični izdelek"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:43
msgid ""
"To set up a new physical rental product, go to the :menuselection:`Rental "
"app --> Products`, then click :guilabel:`New`. On the rental product form, "
"fill out each tab accordingly:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti nov fizični najemni izdelek, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`aplikacija Najem --> Izdelki`, nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo`. Na obrazcu najemnega izdelka ustrezno izpolnite vsak "
"zavihek:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:47
msgid "General Information tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Splošne informacije"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:49
msgid ""
"In the new product window, the :guilabel:`Rental` checkbox is already ticked "
"by default. Select the :guilabel:`Product Type` as :guilabel:`Goods`."
msgstr ""
"V novem oknu izdelka je potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Najem` že privzeto "
"označeno. Izberite :guilabel:`Vrsta izdelka` kot :guilabel:`Blago`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:52
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Track Inventory` checkbox and select :guilabel:`By "
"Quantity` from the drop-down menu. For the :guilabel:`Category` field, "
"select :guilabel:`Goods` from the drop-down menu or create a new category by "
"typing in the name and clicking :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Sledenje zalogi` in iz spustnega "
"menija izberite :guilabel:`Po količini`. Za polje :guilabel:`Kategorija` iz "
"spustnega menija izberite :guilabel:`Blago` ali ustvarite novo kategorijo "
"tako, da vnesete ime in kliknete :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:None
msgid "The new product view in the Rental app."
msgstr "Nov pogled izdelka v aplikaciji Najem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:60
msgid "Attributes & Variants tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Atributi in variante"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:63
msgid ""
"The *Variant* feature in the **Inventory** app must be enabled for this tab "
"to display."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija *Varianta* v aplikaciji **Zaloga** mora biti omogočena, da se ta "
"zavihek prikaže."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:65
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then select a default option from "
"the :guilabel:`Attribute` drop-down menu. To create a new one, enter the "
"name, then click :guilabel:`Create and edit…` to :ref:`configure the "
"attribute and its values <products/variants/attributes>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, nato iz spustnega menija "
":guilabel:`Atribut` izberite privzeto možnost. Če želite ustvariti novo, "
"vnesite ime, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi ...`, da "
":ref:`konfigurirate atribut in njegove vrednosti <products/variants/"
"attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:72
msgid "Rental prices tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Cene najema"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:74
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Rental prices` tab and in the :guilabel:`Pricing` "
"section, click :guilabel:`Add a price` to enter a new rental rate. Choose a "
"*pricing period* (:dfn:`the unit of duration of the rental`) in "
"the :guilabel:`Period` column, or create a new pricing period by typing in "
"the name and clicking :guilabel:`Create and edit`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Cene najema` in v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Oblikovanje cen` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj ceno`, da vnesete novo "
"ceno najema. Izberite *cenovalno obdobje* (:dfn:`enota trajanja najema`) v "
"stolpcu :guilabel:`Obdobje` ali ustvarite novo cenovalno obdobje tako, da "
"vnesete ime in kliknete :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:80
msgid ""
"Creating a new pricing period opens a pop-up *Create period* window. Fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Name`, :guilabel:`Duration`, and :guilabel:`Unit`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. The new pricing period automatically applies."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje novega cenovnega obdobja odpre pojavno okno *Ustvari obdobje*. "
"Izpolnite :guilabel:`Ime`, :guilabel:`Trajanje` in :guilabel:`Enota`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`. Novo cenovno obdobje se samodejno uporabi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:0
msgid "Sample of a New Period view in the Rental app."
msgstr "Vzorec pogleda Novo obdobje v aplikaciji Najem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:87
#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:122
msgid ""
"Next, enter the :guilabel:`Price` for that specific :guilabel:`Period`. To "
"apply the configured rental rate to an existing pricelist, click in "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelist` column and select the desired list from the drop-"
"down menu."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite :guilabel:`Ceno` za določeno :guilabel:`Obdobje`. Če želite "
"konfigurirano ceno najema uporabiti za obstoječi cenik, kliknite v stolpec "
":guilabel:`Cenik` in iz spustnega menija izberite želeni seznam."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:91
#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:126
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Reservations` section, fill in the :guilabel:`Hourly "
"Fine`, :guilabel:`Daily Fine`, and the :guilabel:`Reserve product` time. "
"These values are automatically populated from the :guilabel:`Default Delay "
"Costs` section, provided they have been configured in "
"the :menuselection:`Rental app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Rezervacije` izpolnite :guilabel:`Urna kazen`, "
":guilabel:`Dnevna kazen` in čas :guilabel:`Rezerviraj izdelek`. Te vrednosti "
"so samodejno izpolnjene iz razdelka :guilabel:`Privzeti stroški zamude`, če "
"so bili konfigurirani v :menuselection:`Aplikacija Najem --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:96
#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:131
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` icon near the "
"top to save."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Shrani ročno)` blizu "
"vrha, da shranite."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:99
msgid ""
"A bike rental business rents tandem bikes for two hours at the local park. "
"The hourly rental rate for their tandem bikes is $20, but since tandem bikes "
"are popular, they want to set a new price of $35. To ensure the business "
"gets their bikes returned on time, they set the late return fee as $20 per "
"hour and $160 per day ($20 x 8 hrs)."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje za najem koles daje v najem tandeme za dve uri v lokalnem parku. "
"Urna najemnina za njihove tandeme je 20 $, vendar ker so tandemi "
"priljubljeni, želijo nastaviti novo ceno 35 $. Da bi podjetje zagotovilo "
"pravočasno vračilo koles, nastavi zamudnino 20 $ na uro in 160 $ na dan (20 "
"$ x 8 ur)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:104
msgid ""
"Create a new pricing period by navigating to :menuselection:`Rental app --> "
"Configuration --> Rental periods`. Click :guilabel:`New`, then configure the "
"period for `2` hours."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite novo cenovno obdobje tako, da pojdete na "
":menuselection:`aplikacija Najem --> Konfiguracija --> Najemna obdobja`. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, nato konfigurirajte obdobje za `2` uri."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:107
msgid ""
"Navigate to the tandem bike product and in the :guilabel:`Rental prices` tab "
"add the `2` hour period set at `$35`. Manually save to apply changes."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na izdelek tandem kolo in v zavihku :guilabel:`Cene najema` dodajte "
"obdobje `2` uri, nastavljeno na `35 $`. Ročno shranite, da uveljavite "
"spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/products.rst:0
msgid "Sample of a rental product with the custom rental period applied."
msgstr "Vzorec najetega izdelka z uporabljenim obdobjem najema po meri."

