#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:94
msgid "Configure Gelato connector in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje konektorja Gelato v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:96
msgid ""
"In Odoo, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, then scroll to the :guilabel:`Connectors` section. Enable "
"the :guilabel:`Gelato` connector by ticking the checkbox. Next, paste the "
"newly generated API keys and webhook secret key into their respective "
"fields. Once saved, Gelato is available in Odoo **Sales** and **eCommerce** "
"products."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`, nato se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Konektorji`. Omogočite "
"konektor :guilabel:`Gelato` z označitvijo potrditvenega polja. Nato "
"prilepite novo ustvarjene API ključe in skrivni ključ webhooka v ustrezna "
"polja. Ko je shranjeno, je Gelato na voljo v izdelkih Odoo **Sales** in "
"**eCommerce**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:102
msgid "Synchronizing Gelato products with Odoo Sales"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija izdelkov Gelato z Odoo Sales"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:104
msgid ""
"It is recommended to have products already configured in Gelato before "
"configuring them in Odoo. To get the product ID in Gelato, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Templates` page from the side bar menu. Select which product "
"to synchronize in Odoo, then hover over the product card to reveal "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` menu icon. Click "
"the menu icon, then click :guilabel:`Copy Template ID` to copy the product "
"template ID to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je, da so izdelki že konfigurirani v Gelatu, preden jih "
"konfigurirate v Odoo. Za pridobitev ID-ja izdelka v Gelatu pojdite na stran "
":guilabel:`Predloge` iz stranskega menija. Izberite izdelek, ki ga želite "
"sinhronizirati v Odoo, nato premaknite kazalec miške nad kartico izdelka, da "
"se prikaže ikona menija :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tripičja)"
"`. Kliknite ikono menija, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Kopiraj ID predloge`, da "
"kopirate ID predloge izdelka v odložišče."

