msgstr "Sinhronizacija zaključenih naročil."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:32
msgid "Synchronize all confirmed and unshipped orders."
msgstr "Sinhronizacija vseh potrjenih in neodpremljenih naročil."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:35
msgid ""
"Managed by Lazada, and synchronized with a virtual location to track it in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Upravlja Lazada in se sinhronizira z virtualno lokacijo za sledenje v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:35
msgid "Managed in Odoo Inventory app, and synchronized with Lazada."
msgstr "Upravljano v aplikaciji Odoo Inventory in sinhronizirano z Lazado."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:40
msgid "Handled by Lazada."
msgstr "Upravlja Lazada."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:40
msgid "Delivery information is fetched from Lazada, and synchronized in Odoo."
msgstr "Informacije o dostavi se pridobijo iz Lazade in sinhronizirajo v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:46
msgid ""
"The **Lazada Connector** is designed to synchronize sales orders and "
"inventory. Other actions, such as downloading monthly fee reports, handling "
"disputes, or issuing refunds, **must** be managed from the *Lazada Seller "
"Center*, as usual."
msgstr ""
"**Lazada Connector** je zasnovan za sinhronizacijo prodajnih nalogov in "
"zaloge. Druga dejanja, kot so prenos mesečnih poročil o stroških, reševanje "
"sporov ali izdajanje vračil, **je treba** upravljati iz *Lazada Seller "
"Center*, kot običajno."

