msgid "Connect a Lazada Seller account:"
msgstr "Povežite račun Lazada Seller:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:95
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration --> Lazada --> Shops` and "
"click :guilabel:`Create New Shop`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Lazada --> "
"Trgovine` in kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari novo trgovino`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:97
msgid ""
"Enter a name (e.g., \"Lazada Malaysia\"), :guilabel:`App "
"Key`, :guilabel:`App Secret`, and select the marketplace (e.g., "
"Lazada.com.my)."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ime (npr. \"Lazada Malezija\"), :guilabel:`App Key`, :guilabel:`App "
"Secret` in izberite tržnico (npr. Lazada.com.my)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:102
msgid "Link the account by doing the following:"
msgstr "Račun povežite tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:104
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Create Shop & Authorize`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari trgovino in avtoriziraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:105
msgid ""
"Click the button to redirect to the Lazada login or consent page. Log in "
"with your Lazada Seller account credentials and grant Odoo access."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb za preusmeritev na stran za prijavo ali soglasje Lazada. "
"Prijavite se s poverilnicami vašega računa Lazada Seller in dovolite dostop "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:110
msgid ""
"Upon successful authorization, Odoo lists available marketplaces under "
"the :guilabel:`Lazada Shops` tab."
msgstr ""
"Po uspešni avtorizaciji Odoo navede razpoložljive tržnice pod zavihkom "
":guilabel:`Lazada Shops`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:115
msgid "Manage Marketplaces:"
msgstr "Upravljanje tržnic:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:117
msgid ""
"Newly added marketplaces are automatically synchronized. To disable "
"synchronization for specific marketplaces, remove them from the list."
msgstr ""
"Novo dodana tržišča se samodejno sinhronizirajo. Če želite onemogočiti "
"sinhronizacijo za določena tržišča, jih odstranite s seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:119
msgid ""
"Avoid synchronizing the same shop multiple times to prevent duplicate orders."
msgstr ""
"Izogibajte se večkratni sinhronizaciji iste trgovine, da preprečite "
"podvojene naročila."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:123
msgid ""
"To maintain data integrity, ensure each shop is synchronized only once. If "
"synchronization fails, try manually fetching orders before reconfiguring."
msgstr ""
"Za ohranitev celovitosti podatkov zagotovite, da se vsaka trgovina "
"sinhronizira samo enkrat. Če sinhronizacija ne uspe, poskusite ročno "
"pridobiti naročila, preden ponovno konfigurirate."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:127
msgid "Configure the shop before go-live"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte trgovino pred zagonom"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:129
msgid "Set up warehouses:"
msgstr "Nastavite skladišča:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:131
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings --> "
"Connectors --> Lazada --> Lazada Shops`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> Konektorji --> Lazada --> Trgovine Lazada`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:133
msgid ""
"Select the Lazada shop and configure the :guilabel:`FBM Warehouse` field to "
"limit stock fetching to specific warehouses."
msgstr ""
"Izberite trgovino Lazada in konfigurirajte polje :guilabel:`FBM skladišče`, "
"da omejite pridobivanje zaloge na določena skladišča."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:135
msgid ""
"By default, all accounts use the same Lazada stock location. To isolate "
"stock for a specific marketplace, create a separate account registration and "
"assign a unique stock location."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto vsi računi uporabljajo isto skladiščno lokacijo Lazada. Če želite "
"ločiti zalogo za določeno tržišče, ustvarite ločeno registracijo računa in "
"dodelite edinstveno skladiščno lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:139
msgid ""
"To manually trigger re-initialization of the catalog, clear "
"the :guilabel:`Last Catalog Synchronization` before clicking :guilabel:`Sync "
"Catalog`."
msgstr ""
"Za ročno sprožitev ponovne inicializacije kataloga počistite "
":guilabel:`Zadnja sinhronizacija kataloga`, preden kliknete "
":guilabel:`Sinhroniziraj katalog`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:142
msgid "Synchronize the product catalog:"
msgstr "Sinhronizirajte katalog izdelkov:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:144
msgid ""
"The product catalog is automatically matched during the first "
"synchronization. However, it is recommended to synchronize the product "
"catalog in the following scenarios:"
msgstr ""
"Katalog izdelkov se samodejno uskladi med prvo sinhronizacijo. Vendar "
"priporočamo sinhronizacijo kataloga izdelkov v naslednjih primerih:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:147
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Sync Catalog` button in Odoo to automatically fetch "
"active Lazada products daily."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb :guilabel:`Sinhroniziraj katalog` v Odoo za samodejno dnevno "
"pridobivanje aktivnih izdelkov Lazada."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:149
msgid ""
"For new Odoo databases, export the Lazada catalog from *Lazada Seller "
"Center* (including SKUs). Import into Odoo via :menuselection:`Inventory app "
"--> Products --> Import`, mapping SKUs to the :guilabel:`Internal Reference` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Za nove podatkovne baze Odoo izvozite katalog Lazada iz *Prodajnega centra "
"Lazada* (vključno s SKU). Uvozite v Odoo prek :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Zaloga --> Izdelki --> Uvozi` in preslikajte SKU v polje :guilabel:`Notranja "
"referenca`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:152
msgid ""
"For existing Odoo products, export both Lazada and Odoo catalogs, map SKUs "
"to :guilabel:`Internal References` in a spreadsheet, and import the updated "
"mappings back into Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za obstoječe izdelke Odoo izvozite kataloge Lazada in Odoo, povežite SKU-je "
"z :guilabel:`Notranjimi referencami` v preglednici in uvozite posodobljene "
"preslikave nazaj v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/setup.rst:157
msgid ""
"Test catalog synchronization with a small product set to verify SKU mappings "
"before full import."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusite sinhronizacijo kataloga z majhnim naborom izdelkov, da preverite "
"preslikave SKU pred celotnim uvozom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices.rst:5
msgid "Products & Prices"
msgstr "Izdelki in cene"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:3
msgid "Use eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "Uporaba e-denarnic in darilnih kartic"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:5
msgid ""
"With Odoo, customers can use **eWallets** and **gift cards** for online and "
"in-store shopping."
msgstr ""
"Z Odoo lahko stranke uporabljajo **e-denarnice** in **darilne kartice** za "
"spletno in fizično nakupovanje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:7
msgid ""
"To enable eWallets and gift cards for eCommerce and Point of Sale (PoS), "
"first enable :guilabel:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` "
"under :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings --> Pricing "
"section`. Once enabled, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Gift cards & eWallet` and :guilabel:`Create` a new eWallet or gift card "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti e-denarnice in darilne kartice za eCommerce in prodajno "
"točko (PoS), najprej omogočite :guilabel:`Popusti, zvestoba in darilne "
"kartice` pod :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> razdelek Cene`. Ko je omogočeno, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Izdelki --> Darilne kartice in e-"
"denarnica` in :guilabel:`Ustvari` nov program e-denarnice ali darilne "
"kartice."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:13
msgid "eWallets"
msgstr "e-denarnice"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:15
msgid ""
"eWallets allow customers to save credits on their online account and use "
"these credits as a payment method when buying items in an online store or a "
"brick-and-mortar store. eWallets can also be used to centralize "
"multiple :ref:`gift cards <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>`."
msgstr ""
"e-Denarnice strankam omogočajo shranjevanje dobroimetja na njihovem spletnem "
"računu in uporabo tega dobroimetja kot način plačila pri nakupu artiklov v "
"spletni trgovini ali fizični trgovini. e-Denarnice je mogoče uporabiti tudi "
"za centralizacijo več :ref:`darilnih kartic <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:19
msgid ""
"Before creating an eWallet program, it is necessary to create an eWallet "
"**top-up** product. Top-ups are pre-defined digital credit values added to "
"an eWallet in exchange for its equivalent in real currency. These credits "
"can then be used as a payment method in the eCommerce shop or :abbr:`PoS "
"(Point of Sale)`. Top-up values can be of different amounts."
msgstr ""
"Pred ustvarjanjem programa e-denarnice je treba ustvariti izdelek za "
"**dopolnitev** e-denarnice. Dopolnitve so vnaprej določene vrednosti "
"digitalnega dobroimetja, dodanega e-denarnici v zameno za njegov ekvivalent "
"v pravi valuti. To dobroimetje je nato mogoče uporabiti kot način plačila v "
"spletni trgovini ali :abbr:`PoS (prodajni točki)`. Vrednosti dopolnitev so "
"lahko različnih zneskov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:25
msgid ""
"A $50 top-up can be bought for $50, and adds that same amount of credits to "
"the eWallet."
msgstr ""
"Dopolnitev za 50 $ je mogoče kupiti za 50 $ in doda enak znesek dobroimetja "
"v e-denarnico."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:27
msgid ""
"To create a top-up product, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products` and :guilabel:`Create` a new product. On the product template, "
"configure the options as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti izdelek za dopolnitev, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Izdelki --> Izdelki` in "
":guilabel:`Ustvari` nov izdelek. V predlogi izdelka konfigurirajte možnosti "
"na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Name`: enter a name for the top-up product (for example, "
"`$50 Top-Up`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ime izdelka`: vnesite ime za izdelek dopolnitve (na primer "
"`Dopolnitev za 50 $`)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:92
msgid ":guilabel:`Can be Sold`: enabled"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lahko se proda`: omogočeno"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:32
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:93
msgid ":guilabel:`Product Type`: select :guilabel:`Service`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrsta izdelka`: izberite :guilabel:`Storitev`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:94
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`: select :guilabel:`Prepaid/Fixed Price`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pravilnik za izdajo računov`: izberite :guilabel:`Vnaplačilo/"
"fiksna cena`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:95
msgid ":guilabel:`Create on Order`: select :guilabel:`Nothing`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ustvari ob naročilu`: izberite :guilabel:`Nič`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:35
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Price`: enter the amount of the top-up"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prodajna cena`: vnesite znesek dobroimetja"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:38
msgid ""
"In order to have eWallet top-ups of different amounts, create multiple top-"
"up products and modify the :guilabel:`Sales Price` accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Za dobroimetja e-denarne v različnih zneskih ustvarite več izdelkov za "
"dobroimetje in ustrezno spremenite :guilabel:`Prodajno ceno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:41
msgid ""
"Once the top-up is created, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Gift cards & eWallet` to :guilabel:`Create` an eWallet program. The "
