":guilabel:`invoice_partner_country` v predlogi PDF. Po nalaganju PDF v "
"aplikacijo **Prodaja** so nastavili :guilabel:`Pot` za :guilabel:`Ime polja "
"obrazca` na:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:147
msgid ""
"For a header or footer "
"document: :guilabel:`partner_invoice_id.country_id.name`"
msgstr ""
"Za dokument glave ali noge: :guilabel:`partner_invoice_id.country_id.name`"

