msgstr "Primer Odoo poti polja obrazca za državo stranke iz dokumenta izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:164
msgid "Create a custom note form field"
msgstr "Ustvarite polje obrazca za opombo po meri"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:166
msgid ""
"When uploading any PDF containing the form field :guilabel:`custom_note`, "
"leaving the :guilabel:`Path` empty allows the seller to add any note to that "
"form field in the document, which shown when the PDF is built."
msgstr ""
"Pri nalaganju katerega koli PDF, ki vsebuje polje obrazca "
":guilabel:`custom_note`, pustitev :guilabel:`Poti` prazne omogoča "
"prodajalcu, da doda katerokoli opombo temu polju obrazca v dokumentu, kar je "
"prikazano, ko je PDF ustvarjen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:173
msgid "Custom note field name with an empty Path cell."
msgstr "Ime polja za opombo po meri s prazno celico Pot."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:173
msgid ""
"Leave the :guilabel:`Path` column cell empty for the :guilabel:`custom_note` "
"row."
msgstr ""
"Pustite celico stolpca :guilabel:`Pot` prazno za vrstico "
":guilabel:`custom_note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:178
msgid "Quote Builder tab with note field to customize."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek Graditelj ponudb s poljem za opombo, ki ga je mogoče prilagoditi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:178
msgid ""
"The note field in the *Header* section in the :guilabel:`Quote Builder` tab "
"on a quotation."
msgstr ""
"Polje za opombo v razdelku *Glava* v zavihku :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudb` na "
"ponudbi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:183
msgid "Common dynamic form fields"
msgstr "Pogosta dinamična polja obrazcev"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:185
msgid ""
"Below are common dynamic form fields to use in custom PDFs that "
"automatically map to the correct Odoo fields when uploaded to the **Sales** "
"app, and what they represent."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj so navedena pogosta dinamična polja obrazcev za uporabo v PDF po "
"meri, ki se samodejno preslikajo v pravilna polja Odoo, ko so naložena v "
"aplikacijo **Prodaja**, in kaj predstavljajo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:188
msgid "For headers and footers PDF:"
msgstr "Za glavo in nogo PDF:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:190
